 Russia, Mongolia and Guinea, and another about Kim Jong Un's work being posted on an African website.\", \"from\": 3778, \"to\": 4019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3778, \"end\": 3782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_Central_News_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"KCNA\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_Central_News_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_Central_News_Agency\"}, {\"begin\": 3869, \"end\": 3880, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Jong-il\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kim Jong Il\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Jong-il\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Jong-il\"}, {\"begin\": 3918, \"end\": 3924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 5.663065846020021e-12, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 3926, \"end\": 3934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9846539449883924, \"rank\": 0.015585226699822454, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 3965, \"end\": 3976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Jong-un\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kim Jong Un\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Jong-un\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Jong-un\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a report\", \"from\": 3835, \"to\": 3843}, {\"ngram\": \"the anniversary\", \"from\": 3850, \"to\": 3865}, {\"ngram\": \"Guinea\", \"from\": 3939, \"to\": 3945}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\":